H. L. JOHNSTONE, Claimant of the Gas Screw TORNADO, etc., Appellant, v. UNITED STATES of America, Appellee. No. 6970. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 3, 1932.

Before SAWTELLE, Circuit Judge, and ST. SURE, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Upon motion of proctors for appellee, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause} mandate forthwith.
